I have a simple (and possibly only approximative script) that counts for me:

   edd at max:~/svn/rcpp/pkg$ cat ../scripts/countTests.sh 
   #!/bin/bash

   cd Rcpp/inst/unitTests/
   echo -n "Functions: "
   egrep "test.* function\(" runit.*R | wc -l
   echo -n "Tests    : "
