From: cubranic at stat.ubc.ca (Davor Cubranic)
Date: Tue, 28 Aug 2012 21:07:58 -0700
Subject: [Rcpp-devel] Initialize a matrix with a vector and the
	dimensions
In-Reply-To: <CABrM6wmPFHYrWvdGtQfP14=ueMvHZ5pjYnmdrxJtSAGHxdiYGQ@mail.gmail.com>
References: <CABrM6w=6hZ0ZXpnoB6sWQBNZQsxEScCjzRQAggnBK8ymUXvDpw@mail.gmail.com>
