Well, blame Rcpp which does not build there.  Martyn P. once helped with
patches for gcc-on-solaris; nobody but the respective CRAN maintainer seems
to have access to, or care about, sun-cc-on-solaris.

Romain and I always maintained that as long as we do not have shell on such a
